0227#STR0227#ALL#The lack of accuracy of these declarations shall entail sanctions mentioned in articles  
0228#STR0228#ALL#171 and 299 of the Penal Code.
0229#STR0229#ALL#The work accident must be reported up to the 1st working day after the accident,  
0230#STR0230#ALL#on penalty of fine.
0231#STR0231#ALL#The communication of work accident shall be governed by article 134 of Decree no. 2.172/97.
0232#STR0232#ALL#The concepts of work accident and occupational disease are defined in articles 131 and 133 
0233#STR0233#ALL#of Decree nş 2.172/97.
0234#STR0234#ALL#The characterization of accident shall be governed by article 135 of Decree no. 2.172/97.
